The '''Pouffra circuit''' was an amateur [[Podracing/Legends|podracing]] circuit in the [[Pouffra system/Legends|Pouffra system]]. It was notorious for being one of the safest (and, therefore, wimpiest) tracks in the galactic podracing circuit, and consequently, serious professionals competitors looked down on the Pouffra's racers.

A track favorite there was [[Ben Quadinaros/Legends|Ben Quadinaros]].

